review_blob: Liked this a lot. 22oz bottle recommended by HyVee at 158th&Maple;, then consumed at home. Great aroma, huge chocolate. Thick tan head as attractive compliment to rich dark color of the beer. Claims to have strong coffee notes but really only tasted that as a bit of bitterness in the lingering after-taste. Checking website not clear whether more is available, but dropped them a note to hope theyd continue this product and supply it retail outside their somewhat remote location.
